description: The laughingstock of other goblins, who themselves are the laughingstock of everyone else.
sayings:s[|]: The @name pick$ @my nose.|The @name drool$ a little.|The @name point$ and laugh$ at nothing.|The @name belch$$, “[?]Hehe, butts![?]”

description: The toughest goblin... of a group of the weakest goblins. Possibly a threat, maybe? To a toy poodle?
sayings:s[|]: The @name scratch$$ @my rear.|The @name tr$$$ to look tough.|The @name cackle$ nervously.|The @name stutter$, “[?]Uh oh, it's the hero![?]”

description: Bigger than the average human, but a little lacking in the creative thinking department. Seems to like taking orders.
sayings:s[|]: The @name drool$ copiously.|The @name yawn$ somewhat menacingly.|The @name adjust$ @my codpiece... for far too long.|The @name bark$, “[?]I got this bro![?]”

description: A pyromaniac hobgoblin who loves to throw bombs, perhaps to the detriment of his sneakier allies.
sayings:s[|]: The @name burn$ @my own hair a little.|The @name imitate$ explosion noises!|The @name cackle$ maniacally.|The @name holler$, “[?]Oh yeah broski![?]”

description: The boss around here, or so he says. Bigger than other hobgoblins, which is probably why they listen to him.
sayings:s[|]: The @name grumble$ loudly.|The @name scowl$ at the ground.|The @name strike$ a pose!|The @name shout$, “[?]Get em brochachos![?]”

description: Like a lion... from Hell. Big pointy teeth, serious claws, and fire magic.
sayings:s[|]: The @name growl$...|The @name hiss$$ with scorching breath!|The @name purr$ with sinister pleasure.|The @name arch$$ @my back and roar$!

description: A mobile slime mold the size of a small dog.
A large squishy with a wild tangle of hardened bits that act as antlers for fighting.
A very large squishy that actively seeks out organics to break down into food for its herd.
A human who specializes in raising and caring for squishy.
sayings:s[|]: The @name scatter$ chum for the squishies!|The @name pine$ for @my homeland...|The @name attempt$ to call @my squishy herd!|The @name shriek$, “[?]Eek![?]”

description: An elf who seems very happy, ecstatic actually, while blasting the surroundings with magic.
sayings:s[|]: The @name stare$ into infinite space...|The @name dance$ spasmodically!|The @name attempt$ a drum solo without drums!|The @name looks amazed and whispers, “[?]Dude...[?]”
